HASHCAT - Settings
If you are using Hashcat for the first time, errors may occur if the correct drivers are not installed for the CPU and GPU. If you receive the following message:
"ATTENTION! No OpenCL or CUDA installation found. You are probably missing the CUDA or OpenCL runtime installation."
install the specified drivers:
* AMD GPUs on Windows require this driver: "AMD Radeon Adrenalin 2020 Edition" (20.2.2 or later)
* Intel CPUs require this runtime: "OpenCL Runtime for Intel Core and Intel Xeon Processors" (16.1.1 or later)
* NVIDIA GPUs require this runtime and/or driver (both): "NVIDIA Driver" (440.64 or later) "CUDA Toolkit" (9.0 or later)
Further information under: https://hashcat.net/faq/wrongdriver
